# API Stability Channels

{/* AUTO-GENERATED FILE - DO NOT EDIT DIRECTLY. Edit the source document instead: src/content/docs/docs/api-stability.mdx Then run: pnpm generate-language-pages */}

import { LinkButton } from "@astrojs/starlight/components";

Genkit follows [semantic versioning](https://semver.org/). Genkit Python is currently in Alpha (`0.*`),
so bug fixes and new features happening in patch releases and breaking changes in minor releases.
